definition: whether or not/can it or can't it/is it possible?
can/to be able to/might possibly/ability/(physics) energy

sentences.english: Can you apply that outside of high-traffic Web sites?
sentences.chinese: 能否把這樣的方法應用到大規模流量網站之外的應用？

sentences.english: All night long, you can feel my heart palpitates.
sentences.chinese: 長夜漫漫，你能否感覺我的心跳。

sentences.english: Can we stop using the unrecyclable style of lunch boxes?
sentences.chinese: 我們能否停止使用不可回收的快餐盒？

sentences.english: Can no multidisc games be put in a package with this?
sentences.chinese: 單碟遊戲能否像這樣封裝在一起？

sentences.english: Turn that moment, www. qqtubiao5. cn can you see I dropped tears.
sentences.chinese: 回身那一刻你能否看到了我掉的淚。

sentences.english: How can they control what pops up on the Internet?
sentences.chinese: 他們能否控制互聯網上的彈出消息？

sentences.english: I've filled in this form incorrectly. Can I have another blank?
sentences.chinese: 這張表我填錯了，能否再給我一張空白表格？

sentences.english: Can Declan come to visit me?
Your Petals season, can see my tears?
sentences.chinese: 你的落花時節，能否看到我的眼淚？

sentences.english: If the Shanghai Customs determines there is infringement, can it impose any fine or penalty against the infringer?
sentences.chinese: 當發現侵權後，上海海關能否對侵權者罰款？

sentences.english: The main concern is, whether those cartoonists are able to carry on their carrers as artists, just as they have been before?
sentences.chinese: 漫畫家能否再像以前一樣，作爲藝術家而生存？

sentences.english: Can they feel the  crackle of  electricity in the wind?
sentences.chinese: 他們能否感受到風中的電光火石？

sentences.english: Could this lead to the death of the comb-over?
sentences.chinese: 這樣能否導致上櫛狀體死亡呢？

sentences.english: Now let us see if we can find out what this is.
sentences.chinese: 現在讓我們看看我們能否發現那是些什麼東西。

sentences.english: CYP 11B2 mRNA expression was identified in the liver and lung of rats.
sentences.chinese: 確定肝臟和肺臟能否合成醛固酮。

sentences.english: I am writing to find out the possibility of our having a brief meeting some time next week…
sentences.chinese: 我去信詢問一下我們能否在下週某個時間見面。

definition: (posing a question: whether sb, something) can or cannot?/is able to or not
to be capable of/to be able to/can
lit. to wipe one's eyes and wait (idiom); to wait and see
can/to be able to/might possibly/ability/(physics) energy
auxiliary verb introducing future action: may (be able to)/will (cause)/should (enable)/going to
to go to the bottom of a matter/after all/when all is said and done/(in an interrogative sentence) finally/outcome/result
